security.name: ASML Holding N.V. - Depositary Receipt (Common Stock)
security.description: ASML Holding N.V. is a multinational corporation based in the Netherlands, primarily operating within the semiconductor industry. Notably, ASML is distinguished as a pioneering supplier of photolithography equipment, essential for the manufacturing of integrated circuits or chips. Its technology is critical for advancing Moore's Law, focusing on the development of extreme ultraviolet (EUV) lithography machines, which are paramount in producing smaller, more powerful, and energy-efficient semiconductors. ASML's innovations not only drive the next generation of microchip technology but also underpin major growth trends in sectors such as data processing, telecommunications, and consumer electronics. The company's strategic projects and technology developments are integral to the semiconductor value chain, reflecting its premier position in a highly specialized and competitive market.
